    ** Navigation classes moved to <a>
    ** Classes: 
    **   	'root' => the first link (top level)
    **		'active' => the active link
    **		'active-parent' => the parent of the active link
    **		'active-ancestor' => similar to 'active-parent' but higher up
    **		'has-children' => the item has a further sub menu
    **		'no-children'  => item is the last of branch.
    -->

